text:
Search for: Feb 10 2017 SHOCK IMAGE: Actress Juliette Lewis Has Wardrobe Malfunction On Fashion Week Runway . . . Exposes Her WRINKLE PUSS To The CROWD!! February 10, 2017 : Juliette Lewis walked the runway at the American Heart Association’s Go Red For Women Red Dress Collection 2017 presented by Macy’s at Fashion Week in New York City at Hammerstein Ballroom. And she had a wardrobe malfunction with her dress. It did not appear that she was wearing anything underneath either.
As you van imagine . . . onlookers were SHOCKED!!
